    dc:creator "Yang, Qin-Er", "Yuan, Qiong" ;
    dc:date "2023" ;
    dc:title "Taxonomic studies on the genus Delphinium (Ranunculaceae) from China (XXVI): Notes on D. altissimum and D. scabriflorum, with description of a new species, D. pseudoscabriflorum" ;
    bibo:endPage "39" ;
    bibo:issue "1" ;
    bibo:journal "Phytotaxa" ;
    bibo:pubDate "2023-12-12" ;
    bibo:startPage "21" ;
    bibo:volume "630" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10361855>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10361861>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10361871>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10361875>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10361900>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10361904>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10361906>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10361908>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10361912> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10361855>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Selected specimens from Bhutan cited as Delphinium scabriflorum by Munz (1968). A. R.E. Cooper 4114 (BM). B. R.E. Cooper 4114 (E). C. R.E. Cooper 4223 (BM). D. R.E. Cooper 4223 (E). Note that only the two sheets of the collection R.E. Cooper 4114 (A, B) belong to D. scabriflorum while the two sheets of the collection R.E. Cooper 4223 (C, D) belong to D. pseudoscabriflorum sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10361855/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10361861>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Four specimens from Bhutan cited as Delphinium scabriflorum by Munz (1968).A. F. Ludlow & G. Sherriff 219 (BM). B. F. Ludlow & G. Sherriff 219 (E). C, D. F. Ludlow & G. Sherriff 3342 (BM). Note that they should all belong to D. pseudoscabriflorum sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10361861/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10361871>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Holotype (A) and isotype (B–D) sheets of Delphinium pseudoscabriflorum sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10361871/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10361875>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Isotype (A–D) sheets of Delphinium pseudoscabriflorum sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10361875/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10361900>
    dc:description "FIGURE 13. Distribution of Delphinium pseudoscabriflorum sp. nov. (●)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10361900/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10361904>
    dc:description "FIGURE 14. Paratype sheets of Delphinium ludlowii. A. R.E. Cooper 4322 (BM). B. F. Ludlow & G. Sherriff 368 (BM). C. F. Ludlow & G. Sherriff 470 (BM). D. F. Ludlow & G. Sherriff 470 (E)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10361904/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10361906>
    dc:description "FIGURE 15. Holotype (A) and isotype (B) sheets of Delphinium ludlowii. A. F. Ludlow & G. Sherriff 894 (BM). B. F. Ludlow & G. Sherriff 894 (E)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10361906/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10361908>
    dc:description "FIGURE 16. Paratype sheets of Delphinium ludlowii. A. F. Ludlow & G. Sherriff 1008 (BM). B. F. Ludlow & G. Sherriff 16972 (BM). C. F. Ludlow & G. Sherriff 19485 (BM). D. F. Ludlow & G. Sherriff 20978 (BM)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10361908/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10361912>
    dc:description "FIGURE 17. Two specimens from Bhutan identified as Delphinium ludlowii but actually belonging to D. pseudoscabriflorum sp. nov.A. F. Ludlow & G. Sherriff 21303 (BM). B. S.B. Lyon 3480 (BM)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10361912/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

